Introduction

Xu Yang YuZhuo (Korean: 에리와, 쉬양위저; simplified Chinese: 许杨玉琢 | traditional Chinese; 許楊玉琢) is a Chinese idol singer. She is a member of Team HII of Chinese idol group SNH48, and its sub-unit 7SENSES.

She participated on Chinese survival show Youth with You 2 (2020) and ranked 30th in the final round.

Team History:
[2014.07.26] - Joined SNH48 as a Research Student.
[2014.09.05] - Promoted to SNH48 Team HII (Team HII formation)
[2017.04.07] - Joined SNH48 sub-unit 7SENSES.
